n had been expected to push Peaty to the line but, as that challenge faded, Peaty looked on course for the gold only to be agonisingly pipped.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2460, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.6298025098785821, \"rank\": 0.48118604646822055, \"text\": \"Qin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has talked very publicly of the spiral he endured in the wake of Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2674, \"end\": 2679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9496800493351161, \"rank\": 0.052986214314004396, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alluding to what he had gone through, he said: \\\"It's just incredibly hard.\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To win it once, and to win it again, and to win it again.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And to try and find new ways to win it.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything I have done to this point has happened for a reason.\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am so happy I can race the best in the world and come second.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not have done more.\\\"\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Max Litchfield suffered the agony of finishing fourth for a third successiveOlympic Gamesin the final of the men's 4x100m individual medley.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3017, \"end\": 3031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Litchfield\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Litchfield\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Litchfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Litchfield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the event belonged to France's Leon Marchand, billed as the new Phelps of the pool with Phelps fittingly inside the venue.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3185, \"end\": 3191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998305066389271, \"rank\": 0.00016209902022038783, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3199, \"end\": 3207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.99980887325985, \"rank\": 0.00019116132689295522, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 3227, \"end\": 3233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999893566384, \"rank\": 1.0642915266905098e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 3251, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999893566384, \"rank\": 1.0642915266905098e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Frenchman, trained in the US by Phelps' former coach Bob Bowman, just missed out on the world record but eclipsed Phelps' long-standing Olympic mark.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3317, \"end\": 3319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999313755680218, \"rank\": 5.434518038783009e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3323, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999893566384, \"rank\": 1.0642915266905098e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 3344, \"end\": 3347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.5404019710224142, \"rank\": 0.44975036784180095, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 3348, \"end\": 3354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9988422661664339, \"rank\": 0.0011584930947166983, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 3405, \"end\": 3411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999893566384, \"rank\": 1.0642915266905098e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The noise was deafening inside the 15,000-seater stadium, chants of \\\"Leon\\\" ringing out and shouts of \\\"Allez\\\" every time he popped out of the water during the breaststroke leg.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, Litchfield, close to tears, said: \\\"Gutted.\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3631, \"end\": 3641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Litchfield,_Connecticut\", \"score\": 0.8486969434620548, \"rank\": 0.07421088713204915, \"text\": \"Litchfield\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Litchfield,_Connecticut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Litchfield,_Connecticut\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have given absolutely everything, emotionally, mentally, physically.\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have given a best time and it's just tough.\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just the wrong side of it again.\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's sport, that's life.\\\"\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Duncan Scott qualified second fastest for Monday's final of the 200m freestyle and declared it would need the swim of his life to take down David Popivici.\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 4008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3853, \"end\": 3865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9913273362707572, \"rank\": 0.004373974849644039, \"text\": \"Duncan Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Matt Richards looked a littl